RawLine: QINFO_20115,把趙妽準備的三種陷阱：麻繩網、偽裝物、鐵蒺藜。分別設置在適合的地方，以發揮效果、克敵致勝。,把赵妽准备的三种陷阱：麻绳网、伪装物、铁蒺藜。分别设置在适合的地方，以发挥效果、克敌致胜。

Items.mt: Gather the three types of traps prepared by Zhao Li: twine nets, camouflage, and thistles. The three types of traps that Zhao Qi has prepared: the twine net, the camouflage, and the thistles, are set up in the right places to be effective and to defeat the enemy.
